arket stocks surged as US-Iran ceasefire boosted risk appetite. Nippon AMC rose 10.9%, HDFC AMC 8.6%, and BSE 8.3%.\nAnalysts expect AMCs like CAMS to outperform peers despite MTM pressures. Ceasefire seen as positive, though markets remain event-driven.","summary":"Capital market stocks surged as US-Iran ceasefire boosted risk appetite. Nippon AMC rose 10.9%, HDFC AMC 8.6%, and BSE 8.3%.\nAnalysts expect AMCs like CAMS to outperform peers despite MTM pressures. Ceasefire seen as positive, though markets remain event-driven.","url":"https://www.business-standard.com/markets/news/capital-market-stocks-rally-bse-hdfc-amc-us-iran-ceasefire-126040800527_1.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-04-08T13:01:13","source":"Business Standard"},{"id":"563359","title":"HDFC AMC's Navneet Munot expects record SIP inflows amid Iran-US ceasefire, urging retail investors to stay disciplined.\nMunot advises enhancing equity allocation during volatility, citing March SIP inflows to hit all-time high per AMFI data.","summary":"HDFC AMC's Navneet Munot expects record SIP inflows amid Iran-US ceasefire, urging retail investors to stay disciplined.\nMunot advises enhancing equity allocation during volatility, citing March SIP inflows to hit all-time high per AMFI data.","url":"https://www.ndtvprofit.com/personal-finance/iran-war-ceasefire-hdfc-amcs-navneet-munot-expects-record-sip-inflows-11326462#publisher=newsstand","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-04-08T09:28:44","source":"NDTV Profit"},{"id":"557316","title":"HDFC Asset Management to hold a Q4 FY26 results call on April 16, 2026.\nThe call will feature key executives and provide audited financial results review.","summary":"HDFC Asset Management to hold a Q4 FY26 results call on April 16, 2026.\nThe call will feature key executives and provide audited financial results review.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=ed8a29df-d8ef-4c25-bc4b-dfbabd6d805c.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-04-06T12:06:53","source":"BSE"},{"id":"556687","title":"Kotak expects better returns from HDFC AMC than ICICI Prudential AMC due to valuation corrections.\nHDFC AMC has a 17% upside, while ICICI AMC sees 11%. Both focus on growth in alternatives and strong fund performance.","summary":"Kotak expects better returns from HDFC AMC than ICICI Prudential AMC due to valuation corrections.\nHDFC AMC has a 17% upside, while ICICI AMC sees 11%. Both focus on growth in alternatives and strong fund performance.","url":"https://www.ndtvprofit.com/markets/icici-prudential-amc-vs-hdfc-amc-kotak-sees-higher-upside-on-this-stock-11313127#publisher=newsstand","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-04-05T10:29:39","source":"NDTV Profit"},{"id":"260406188343756","title":"March quarter AMC profits may fall sequentially due to MTM losses and softer yields, despite steady inflows.\nICICI Pru and Nippon AMC lead growth, while UTI AMC and Canara Robeco AMC lose market share amid performance gaps.","summary":"March quarter AMC profits may fall sequentially due to MTM losses and softer yields, despite steady inflows.\nICICI Pru and Nippon AMC lead growth, while UTI AMC and Canara Robeco AMC lose market share amid performance gaps.","url":"https://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/markets/march-quarter-amc-profits-could-fall-sequentially-amid-volatility-even-as-annual-growth-remains-healthy-13880528.html/amp","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-04-05T06:00:28","source":"Moneycontrol"},{"id":"552122","title":"HDFC AMC executed an NSE block trade worth Rs. 32.02 crore.\nThe trade involved 138,049 shares at Rs. 2319.6 per share.","summary":"HDFC AMC executed an NSE block trade worth Rs. 32.02 crore.\nThe trade involved 138,049 shares at Rs. 2319.6 per share.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-04-01T12:53:16","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"544791","title":"HDFC AMC sees USD 69M inflows from MSCI Nifty semi-annual rebalancing.\nNifty index reshuffle at 3 PM today may impact HDFC AMC.","summary":"HDFC AMC sees USD 69M infl